r />\n<br />\n今日獨力支撐香港<br />\n明日全民皆兵反抗<br />\n忠勇之光 光復香港<br />\n<br />\n以上可以作100個"},{"pid":"0481514316b16ead9ca45508016260988925a2f4","tid":1814373,"uid":273218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8e39e4fb830ce0305c9fe99f4e414736f5ed38ce","tid":1814373,"uid":55955,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"90d5097f3d5e624c30b9004e0a606df8e6adcbe8","tid":1814373,"uid":224479,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T01:37:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔肯接受現實"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T01:42:57.000Z","msg":"有勇武退場我信，但係唔信咁on9開post話自己係勇武<br />\n經過屠龍小隊比人上門拘捕仲咁高調，唔係鬼就應該係腦殘"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T01:47:44.000Z","msg":"咪就係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一堆分化退場post"},{"pid":"b862a65af159b8e2920abb46b12d086ec4e8911a","tid":1814373,"uid":65072,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8e39e4fb830ce0305c9fe99f4e414736f5ed38ce","tid":1814373,"uid":55955,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"90d5097f3d5e624c30b9004e0a606df8e6adcbe8","tid":1814373,"uid":224479,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T01:37:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔肯接受現實"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T01:42:57.000Z","msg":"有勇武退場我信，但係唔信咁on9開post話自己係勇武<br />\n經過屠龍小隊比人上門拘捕仲咁高調，唔係鬼就應該係腦殘"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T01:52:13.000Z","msg":"果啲連頭盔都唔戴既想點<br />\n例如自認係爆某某玻璃勇武"},{"pid":"a4718bf8228346234ad34e20680311ab1ecc7ab7","tid":1814373,"uid":1327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T01:54:00.000Z","msg":"其實真正既抗爭者已經唔睇連登<br />\n得番d 終極和理非睇<br />\n所有先咁易動搖<br />\n半年都